# MATLAB Agentic Toolkit

This workspace uses the sibling clone at `../matlab-agentic-toolkit/` (parent: `Projects/`).

For MATLAB tasks, read the appropriate `SKILL.md` there (setup, testing, debugging, apps, Live Scripts, etc.). Skills are also symlinked under `~/.agents/skills/` on this machine.

Use the `matlab` MCP server when available (`evaluate_matlab_code`, `run_matlab_file`, `run_matlab_test_file`, `check_matlab_code`, `detect_matlab_toolboxes`).
